@DATABASE "Mantronix"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - M - Mantronix"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - M
                   ====================================

                                 Mantronix
                                 =========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(46175,0)"}          46175,0
@{"Immunity      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(46001,61)"}          46001,61
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(45971,255)")          45971,x (x= 1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
